<h1 id="overview">Getting started</h1>
<p>This app is free to use for the general public. Anyone can sign up using the quick login/signup form that appears at the top of the page for new users.</p>

<h2>Starting a convergent collaboration</h2>
<p>Anyone who has a decision that they wish to address with the convergent facilitation process can start a new collaboration.</p>

<ol>
	<li>From the menu bar, select <span class="click">New</span></li>
	<li>Choose a title, and fill out any important info in under "details"</li>
	<li>If you are using a facilitator, select <span class="click">facilitator mode</span>. (See <a href="#facilitation">facilitation</a> for more info)</li>
	<li>Choose a scoring method (See <a href="#scoring">scoring</a> for more info)</li>
	<li>Click <span class="click">Create</span>. This will generate a page that you can share with anyone you want to invite to the process.</li>
</ol>

<h2>Joining an existing collaboration</h2>
<p>If you visit the link to an existing collaboration, you can click <span class="click">join</span> or just start interacting and you will be automatically added as a collaborator. If you are not logged in when you visit, you will need to use the form that appears at the top of the page to do so. If you enter a username that does not yet exist, a new account will be created for you with that username.</p>

